normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢啲所謂舞臺劇&ldquo;演技&rdquo;<br />\n關埋門自己打飛機算啦<br />\n唔好再格硬搬上電視"},{"pid":"b7171970343daada9839c03f22981f4a7ceb4d58","tid":487483,"uid":20032,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T00:01:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當你話龜頭bob好笑個下我就負皮咗</blockquote><br />\n預撚左俾人負評<br />\n但佢同陳豪我都唔知點解見到就好想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88eb08e86a269d1dfbe44e9d1ec28b0890ce1b48","tid":487483,"uid":2079,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T00:01:52.000Z","msg":"睇 大家好，我係呀輝 入面第2個頂唔順既係泰臣<br />\n屌你以為自己讀過d濕鳩art, 有d舞台經驗, 成個老屎忽格出哂黎"},{"pid":"f898b9b7e3e124d0e259edf3a8e68b713aedd9f0","tid":487483,"uid":20032,"like":45,"dislike":4,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T00:01:58.000Z","msg":"張建東算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢咪又係以為自己懷才不遇好好笑"},{"pid":"7fc1db9e0846e2037f9ade5cf142490121f15226","tid":487483,"uid":29070,"like":50,"dislike":2,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T00:03:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張建東算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢咪又係以為自己懷才不遇好好笑</blockquote><br />\n佢個樣冇觀眾緣<br />\n又以為自己好撚風趣幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e233cb24e968d8767bbdf1abe11122fe8ce83c5","tid":487483,"uid":73883,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T00:05:18.000Z","msg":"垃圾台仲有人睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f79530c2a7c8ff4dcdd6f795906e32fd77fa199","tid":487483,"uid":97119,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T00:08:48.000Z","msg":"泰臣真人寸到嘔呀<br />\n成日當自己演技好撚勁<br />\n但只係一個臭寸的矮仔"},{"pid":"2bce19c71be57ccd7fe2f09181a16c9d6a7f51d9","tid":487483,"uid":7814,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T00:14:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶埋啲浮誇舞台劇所謂&ldquo;演技&rdquo;上電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本係個錯誤 每次睇只會覺得尷尬 快啲過主啦<br />\n<br />\n詹瑞文更加垃圾<br />\n以為自己好搞笑  其實好無聊<br />\n做埋啲扮下乸聲扮女人 搞下食字 再加啲誇張表情 以為咁叫好笑好成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢啲所謂舞臺劇&ldquo;演技&rdquo;<br />\n關埋門自己打飛機算啦<br />\n唔好再格硬搬上電視</blockquote><br />\n擺明想抄jim carrey<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但人地高大靚仔做就話搞笑姐<br />\n你咁撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得詹瑞文搞笑果d 好多都係睇有線兒童台大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da11da5f8062a18d11061d93891dcf2c3c26d810","tid":487483,"uid":20390,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T00:37:23.000Z","msg":"一睇到個topic本身好撐樓主，入到來屌係到吹奏詹端文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4242f3bdcb5d969257cba91cf14ff7a351bb40","tid":487483,"uid":132587,"like":84,"dislike":2,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T00:42:45.000Z","msg":"同樣讀演藝出身<br />\n張繼聰同白只就叫識做戲啦"},{"pid":"5962870440035ccafd5aee276c92092f467e6ab2","tid":487483,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T00:48:12.000Z","msg":"憎詹瑞文多d"},{"pid":"3d33678e6f7fcd7dd446972158f1355d002258b6","tid":487483,"uid":7729,"like":15,"disl