ormal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上次台慶扮司儀面試果PART, 蝦頭出黎勁認真唱粵劇, 又長又悶搞到個場DEAD哂<br />\n泰臣出埋黎又死唔斷氣, 曾志偉都認真救場想趕佢地走, 佢地仲唔識做係要做埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反到農夫出場第一句真全場爆笑, 無冷場<br />\n<br />\n岩岩東華個蝦頭扮武則天唱哂成首<br />\n唔搞笑己經算, 諗住你認真唱會好啲啦, 哇屌你難聽到好似鬼食泥咁<br />\n後尾訪問仲話佢七點開始練到一點幾, 係咪想紅想到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTVB咁多下把藝人 : 農夫, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阿BOB</span>, 細細粒, 何遠東, 張建東呢啲<br />\n起碼知道人地睇佢係為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搞笑</span>, 真係交足功課<br />\n唔似得泰臣同蝦頭呢兩條友以為自己懷才不遇, 做親綜藝表演都做到有偶像包袱咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比d 掌聲黎聽下先"},{"pid":"d083dc9534cc645343d6cccf37df7148a84d3fd4","tid":487483,"uid":31423,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T05:16:21.000Z","msg":"泰臣no comment<br />\n蝦頭好撚煩，成日想搏出位，做獨腳戲，以為聚光燈射住自己一個咁。好似打<br />\n開籃球走嚟踢波仲要獨食咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   果種自負自我真係隔住個mon 都感覺到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdfece75471907224724ffa42267b8d1639747e8","tid":487483,"uid":3735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T05:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收到風樓主叫阿輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得d同事好nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c90bca1100f75448df0119b7ffca7ff0da61d28","tid":487483,"uid":134484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"件蝦頭真係好撚趕客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse